{"id": "33ade8d0412f0cdf985f828adebd328f14636cb659cd6ac28a097333a59037ff", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:0", "text": "Produces a triple output from a single float input. The single float"}
{"id": "c96c6d5be8d08a12e7b5cdc1b207fa6b2430974c86803d8891675e76fd992c20", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:1", "text": "input"}
{"id": "6720b03100cb46e9561b511bf5858918a96b71fd47775cc606d86552cacfb767", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:2", "text": "is copied to each channel. If float"}
{"id": "6416c35cadb931d11c7e981c62cacd81567289d19105c17bbeb9f7f6c11418d6", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:3", "text": "inputR"}
{"id": "4d1a05bd5dc7188f5a22056cd3f242e84ac2e4ef0d7a21311c71ea99e618e085", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:4", "text": "inputG"}
{"id": "b7686ae41a31ccc3db28939d8702fb6c2f31893852e3d8dfe6096d43cdc0f7c6", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:5", "text": "inputB"}
{"id": "1ce79bd4930d35abd8d984d86820bbbf5d78cc4f81ac1fb5f98b9a1619945d76", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:6", "text": "are connected, then those will be convert to a color instead"}
{"id": "36ecb4f8669133ce744c21982ba4abe2ecd7086e1dc2226ccd6f266f3a5005f8", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:8", "text": "Input"}
{"id": "e7a5de3b2aa097f5c2273fe01381780198c8626bc3a8e302dd36b72fbf48d6a1", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:9", "text": "The float to convert to a triple."}
{"id": "ae09b3c8f29813aa423c3a8167d956ff183221964407ef1dafe9b680ad34dbc0", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:10", "text": "Input R"}
{"id": "5d8772053b7cf487a92ff16bbe84d634d6058f39e3e26c1acfc9ab0bf05921bd", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:11", "text": "The float to place in the R component of"}
{"id": "d2ce36df8d9d8ca423058bd611be74fd4aac8c7b788f60048dcccc7fd43964fb", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:14", "text": "Input G"}
{"id": "0ad99cf091e5b3ba541742714113964b2d693ec378c5d0025d7e9ae53e616808", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:15", "text": "The float to place in the G component of"}
{"id": "d7bd3eea05c9a2cc0cff44c3bb603e778b7cee64daec6d07a620e74a8bc4bcbe", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:18", "text": "Input B"}
{"id": "7510f7cdd798d993b25104496e3391810dfaee78f0cd3819a77496bb1a63a3e0", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:19", "text": "The float to place in the B component of"}
{"id": "7d6df2b2d596f6a595678e8c8a80cac516baa57e9e272683399709717ff4d475", "item_id": "118fa9dd01:24", "text": "The float result copied to R, G, and B."}
